00:00:00.460 --> 00:00:02.860
Hello everyone! Virtual YouTuber Kizuna Ai here!

00:00:02.860 --> 00:00:07.120
I know it's sudden, but, do you know "Salaryman Senryu"?
(Small poems that are usually comical in nature, focused on human existence)

