They start accepting applications everytime when winter starts, right?

00:00:09.660 --> 00:00:13.460
It turns out that the winning works will receive a prize in cash!

00:00:13.460 --> 00:00:16.080
And appear in different medias

00:00:17.020 --> 00:00:19.945
If I get the prize and become more famous...

00:00:19.945 --> 00:00:23.080
A lot more people will know me! Right?

00:00:23.080 --> 00:00:26.680
Goood! I’ll work hard to make the most prized work!

