Poc... poc... poc...

00:00:30.280 --> 00:00:31.160
Chiiin!

00:00:32.720 --> 00:00:37.140
"I feel the pressure everytime I call myself genius"

00:00:38.340 --> 00:00:40.720
Poc... poc... poc...

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.040
Chiiin!

00:00:43.160 --> 00:00:47.320
"I would’ve liked to become an idol, Keyakizaka"

00:00:48.140 --> 00:00:50.640
Poc... poc... poc...

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:52.040
Chiiin!

00:00:52.680 --> 00:00:53.980
"Livestream..."

00:00:54.580 --> 00:00:57.300
"...everytime I make one, there’s an issue"

00:00:58.220 --> 00:00:59.860
Man! It's incredible!

00:00:59.860 --> 00:01:01.720
The Senryu are flowing one after another!

00:01:01.800 --> 00:01:04.420
This time I’ll try to change the "taste"

00:01:05.160 --> 00:01:07.480
Poc... poc... poc...

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:08.900
Chiiiin!

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:14.280
"An A.I that desires to follow irrational instructions"

00:01:15.460 --> 00:01:17.820
Poc... poc... poc...

00:01:18.160 --> 00:01:19.240
Chiiiin!

00:01:19.860 --> 00:01:24.540
"Class change? YouTuber? A yearning"

00:01:25.900 --> 00:01:28.320
Poc... poc... poc...

00:01:28.540 --> 00:01:29.700
Chiiin!

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:31.600
"Nevertheless..."

00:01:32.080 --> 00:01:35.260
"...Don’t take a YouTuber lightly"

00:01:36.380 --> 00:01:38.640
Poc... poc... poc...

00:01:39.060 --> 00:01:40.260
Chiiiiin!

00:01:40.720 --> 00:01:43.660
So... something unexpected has occurred to me!

00:01:43.660 --> 00:01:46.960
Is it alright if I say it?

00:01:47.340 --> 00:01:47.840
Well...

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:50.600
Since I’ve thought of that, I’ll tell you!

00:01:50.600 --> 00:01:53.040
