00:01:55.520 --> 00:01:56.740
"16 years..."

00:01:57.560 --> 00:02:00.320
"...Right in the middle of a salaryman"

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:04.620
Man! Don’t you think I read some very good Senryu?

00:02:04.780 --> 00:02:07.500
In that case, I’ll apply immediately!

00:02:07.500 --> 00:02:08.640
Let's see...

